dom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/least-punished-in-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":866,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jahannam: The least punished man in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most lightly punished of the people of Hellfire on the Day of Resurrection is a man under whose feet are placed two hot coals by which his brain boils.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6561,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2087,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/17\/no-obedience-creator\/","url_meta":{"origin":866,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Obedience: No obeying creation if disobeying the Creator","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no obedience to anyone if it is disobedience to Allah. Verily, obedience is only in good conduct.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7257, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1840 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u064d\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026